==English==

===Noun===
'''hen'''  (''plural:'' '''[[hens]]''')
# A female [[bird]].
# (''specifically'') A female [[chicken]], especially one kept for its [[egg]]s.
# ''(UK Scottish - and maybe Newcastle? - colloquial)'' term of address for a woman.

